<br>
In terms of cost of the spell, don't compare it to res, compare it to BOA.  It's about the same mana.  Would most clerics sit in Nexxus and continually cast BOA for dots?  Doubt it, that sucks up mana that they will cause them to have to wait when they have a group.<br>
<br>
I will often trade C3 for other buffs, C3 for POTC and SOE to a druid or C3 for Symbol to Cleric or C3 for ModRod and Ring to Mage.  I start my day with those three trades if I am soloing.<br>
